= SDL_GetWindowSize =
Use this function to get the size of the window's client area.


== Syntax ==
```c++
void SDL_GetWindowSize(SDL_Window* window,
                       int*        w,
                       int*        h)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''window'''
|the type used to identify the window
|-
|'''w'''
|the width of the window
|-
|'''h'''
|the height of the window
|}

